Class AbstractFlowSinkSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.infoflow.methodSummary.data.sourceSink.AbstractFlowSinkSource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlowClear, FlowSink, FlowSource

    public abstract class AbstractFlowSinkSource
extends Object
    Data class which stores the data associated to a Sink or a Source of a method flow.
